{"build_type":"library","module_name":"emit-runtime-name-link-into-slot","package_name":"emit-runtime-name-link-into-slot","description":"Lowering helper: emit the low-ops that resolve a package NAME to a runnable address at RUNTIME through the linker, placing the result in dest_slot. Mirrors how a string literal lowers (content-hashed __str label + dataptr) to materialise the name as a cstring in name_slot and registers the string constant, then emits a call to link-name-returning-address(name) whose result goes to dest_slot. Used by the launch lowerings so a launch target is loaded on demand by name instead of being statically linked (load_fn_addr) into the launcher.","function_definitions":{"emit-runtime-name-link-into-slot":{"return_type":"i64","parameter_definitions":[{"parameter_name":"ops","parameter_type":"i64"},{"parameter_name":"name_text","parameter_type":"i64"},{"parameter_name":"name_slot","parameter_type":"i64"},{"parameter_name":"dest_slot","parameter_type":"i64"}],"execution_instructions":[{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"zero","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":0},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"k_name","variable_type":"str","assignment_operation":"string","source_target":"name"},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"k_type","variable_type":"str","assignment_operation":"string","source_target":"type"},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"k_local","variable_type":"str","assignment_operation":"string","source_target":"local"},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"k_str","variable_type":"str","assignment_operation":"string","source_target":"str"},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"k_dataptr","variable_type":"str","assignment_operation":"string","source_target":"dataptr"},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"k_dest","variable_type":"str","assignment_o